<span id="freeTextContainer9829342602747145622">I’m drawn to these books about crazy religious cults. 🤷🏼‍♀️ I live in Utah, so I’ve seen polygamist families in the community. The women are always so quiet and quick to look away. It’s sad, that they have very little confidence and are entirely codependent to their ‘priesthood holder’. 👎🏻They are born into a life of subservient values and know nothing else. It’s all just kinda sad.<br/><br/>She tells a pretty crazy story- very unbelievable how they lived and what they believe. As a mother- no way in hell</span>
  <span id="freeText9829342602747145622" style="display:none">I’m drawn to these books about crazy religious cults. 🤷🏼‍♀️ I live in Utah, so I’ve seen polygamist families in the community. The women are always so quiet and quick to look away. It’s sad, that they have very little confidence and are entirely codependent to their ‘priesthood holder’. 👎🏻They are born into a life of subservient values and know nothing else. It’s all just kinda sad.<br /><br />She tells a pretty crazy story- very unbelievable how they lived and what they believe. As a mother- no way in hell would I stick around if anyone touched my kids. My sister wife would get straight up backhanded the moment she touched my kids. But, hooray for her, getting out of that situation! 👏👏👏</span>
