        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer45271494" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1053753569960182526">Interesting -- kind of like watching Cops is interesting. You don&apos;t really like it, but you can&apos;t pull yourself away beause it&apos;s so unbelievable.</span>
